ite TV Actress\u2014Leading Role In A Comedy <small>(2012)</small><br>Nominated\u2014[[Imagen Awards|Imagen Award]] for Best Supporting Actress\u2014Television <small>(2010, 2012\u20132013)</small>\n|-\n|2011\n| ''[[Portlandia (TV series)|Portlandia]]''\n| Beth / Bookstore Customer\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[NTSF:SD:SUV::]]''\n| The Rememberer\n| Episode: \"Wasila Hills Cop\"\n|-\n| 2013\u20132014\n| ''[[The Legend of Korra]]''\n| Eska (voice)\n| 12 episodes\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2013\n| ''[[Drunk History]]''\n| [[Sacagawea]]\n| Episode: \"Nashville\"\n|-\n| ''[[Maron (TV series)|Maron]]''\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"Jen Moves to L.A.\"\n|-\n| 2014\u20132015\n| ''[[Welcome to Sweden (2014 TV series)|Welcome to Sweden]]''\n| Herself\n| 6 episodes\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2015\n| ''[[Golan the Insatiable]]''\n| [[Golan the Insatiable#Main characters|Dylan Beekler]] (voice)\n| 6 episodes \n|-\n| ''[[Castle (TV series)|Castle]]''\n| Lucy (voice)\n| Uncredited<br/>4 episodes\n|-\n|rowspan=5|2016\n| ''[[SpongeBob SquarePants]]''\n| Nocturna (voice)\n| Episode: \"Mall Girl Pearl\"\n|-\n| ''[[Comedy Bang! Bang! (TV series)|Comedy Bang! Bang!]]''\n| Lady Aubrey / Herself\n| Episode: \"Aubrey Plaza Wears a Velvet Off-the-Shoulder Gown With Flowers in Her Hair\"\n|-\n| ''[[RuPaul's Drag Race All Stars (season 2)|RuPaul's Drag Race All Stars]]''\n| Herself (guest judge)\n|Episode: \"Family That Drags Together\"\n|-\n| ''[[Drunk History]]''\n| [[Aaron Burr]]\n| Episode: \"Hamilton\"\n|-\n| ''[[HarmonQuest]]''\n| Hawaiian Coffee\n| Episode: \"Manoa Prison Hole\"\n|-\n| 2016\u20132020\n| ''[[Criminal Minds]]''\n| Cat Adams\n| 4 episodes \n|-\n| 2017\u20132019\n| ''[[Legion (TV series)|Legion]]''\n| [[Shadow King|Amahl Farouk / Shadow King]]<br/>[[Legion (TV series)#Lenny Busker|Lenny Busker]]\n| 27 episodes<br/>Nominated\u2014[[MTV Movie Award for Best Villain]] <small>(2018)</small><br>Nominated\u2014[[Imagen Awards|Imagen Award]] for Best Actress\u2014Television <small>(2018)</small>\n|-\n|